duties_responsibilities.duty: Perform shipping and receiving activities for a Branch location to ensure timely delivery of correct items to customers.
Picking, checking, and shipping items from sales orders, and preparing them for delivery to customers.
Securing packages to prevent damage during shipping and processing customer returns for shipment back to Distribution Center, Fulfillment Center, or supplier.
Sorting, placing, and reporting damaged or substandard inventory items and maintaining a clean and safe working environment.
Possibly delivering items to customers, processing counter sales or invoices, and operating a forklift or similar equipment.
Receiving items in the computer system to maintain availability for customers.
